quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  77,46,"Ẹ jẹ, kí ẹ sì gbádùn fún ìgbà díẹ̀. Dájúdájú ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ ni yín."
  77,47,"Ègbé ni ní ọjọ́ yẹn fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́."
  77,48,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ fún wọn pé kí wọ́n kírun, wọn kò níí kírun."
  79,37,"Nítorí náà, ní ti ẹni tó tayọ ẹnu-ààlà,"
  79,38,"tí ó tún gbé àjùlọ fún ìṣẹ̀mí ayé,"
  79,39,"dájúdájú iná Jẹhīm, òhun ni ibùgbé (rẹ̀)."
  80,34,"ní ọjọ́ tí ènìyàn yóò sá fún arákùnrin rẹ̀,"
  80,35,"àti ìyá rẹ̀ àti bàbá rẹ̀,"
  80,36,"àti ìyàwó rẹ̀ àti àwọn ọmọ rẹ̀."
  83,22,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹni rere máa wà nínú ìgbádùn."
  83,23,"Wọn yóò máa wòran lórí àwọn ibùsùn."
  83,24,"Ìwọ yóò dá ìtutù ojú ìgbádùn mọ̀ nínú ojú wọn."
  84,19,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin yóò máa bọ́ sínú wàhálà kan láti inú wàhálà kan."
  84,20,"Kí l’ó ṣe wọ́n ná tí wọn kò fi gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo?"
  84,21,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sì ké al-Ƙur’ān fún wọn, wọn kò níí forí kanlẹ̀."
  85,16,"Olùṣe-ohun-t’Ó-bá-fẹ́."
  85,17,"Ṣebí ìró àwọn ọmọ ogun ti dé ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ,"
  85,18,"(ọmọ ogun) Fir‘aon àti (ìjọ) Thamūd?"
  86,10,"Nígbà náà, kò níí sí agbára tàbí alárànṣe kan fún un."
  86,11,"Allāhu fi sánmọ̀ tó ń rọ òjò ní ọdọọdún búra."
  86,12,"Ó tún fi ilẹ̀ tó ń sán kànkàn (fún híhùjáde èso) búra."
  87,7,"Àyàfi ohun tí Allāhu bá fẹ́.Dájúdájú Ó mọ gban̄gba àti ohun tó pamọ́. {1}",footnotes:1:Ìyẹn nípasẹ̀ fífí ìdájọ́ kan pa ìdájọ́ tó ṣíwájú rẹ̀ rẹ́. Ẹ wo sūrah al-Baƙọrah;  2:106.
  87,8,"Àwa yó sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere ní ìrọ̀rùn fún ọ."
  87,9,"Nítorí náà, ṣèrántí ní àyè tí ìrántí ti wúlò.1 {1}",footnotes:1:Ìyẹn ni pé, wọ́n fẹ́ kí ṣíṣe ìrántí ọ̀rọ̀ Allāhu jìnnà sí àyè ìhunrírà (bí ilé ọtí), ilé eré àti ilé awàdà nítorí pé, àwọn ènìyàn tó wà níbẹ̀ kò níí kọbi ara sí olùsọ̀rọ̀. Āyah yìí jọ sūrah an-Nisā’;  4:140 àti sūrah al-’Ani‘ām;  6:68.
  88,4,"Wọ́n sì máa wọ inú Iná tó gbóná janjan (ní ọ̀run)."
  88,5,"Wọ́n sì máa fún (wọn) ní omi ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú gbígbóná mu."
  88,6,"Kò sí oúnjẹ kan fún wọn àyàfi igi ẹlẹ́gùn-ún gbígbẹ."
  89,1,"Allāhu fi àfẹ̀mọ́júmọ́ búra."
  89,2,"Ó tún fi àwọn òru mẹ́wàá kan búra."
  89,3,"Ó tún fi n̄ǹkan tí eéjì ń pín geerege àti n̄ǹkan tí eéjì kò pín geerege búra."